---
// src/pages/about.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="About Me | Attachment Matters, LLC" 
    description="Learn about my experience, credentials, and therapeutic approach. I am a relationship-driven, attachment-focused, and trauma-responsive clinician.">
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-sans font-bold text-brand-deep-purple text-center">My Philosophy & Approach</h1>
        
        <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                <!-- You will replace this with your headshot -->
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x400.png/f4d3d3/483248?text=Your+Headshot" alt="Headshot of the therapist" class="rounded-full shadow-lg mx-auto">
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-sans font-semibold text-brand-rust">Warm, Compassionate, and Highly Skilled</h2>
                <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
                    The most critical information you should know about me is that I am a client-centered provider who is also very skilled at what I do. I have **16 years of experience** in the field working with complex family systems and am well-regarded as a skilled professional in the region. 
                </p>
                <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
                    I carry an LCSW (License in Clinical Social Work) and have been licensed for 14 years with no ethical complaints. My approach is relationship-driven, attachment-focused, and trauma-responsive.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-sans font-semibold text-brand-rust text-center">Credentials & Therapeutic Toolbox</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                I have an eclectic style and enjoy utilizing a wide array of evidence-based practices to support children and families. My goal is always to help you achieve better overall functioning and bonding.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-6 grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
                <li class="bg-brand-sand p-3 rounded">Cognitive Behavior Therapy (CBT)</li>
                <li class="bg-brand-sand p-3 rounded">Child Centered Play Therapy</li>
                <li class="bg-brand-sand p-3 rounded">Synergetic Play Therapy (SPT)</li>
                <li class="bg-brand-sand p-3 rounded">Parent Child Interactional Therapy (PCIT)</li>
                <li class="bg-brand-sand p-3 rounded">The Neurosequential Model</li>
                <li class="bg-brand-sand p-3 rounded">Trauma Focused CBT (TF-CBT)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>